					h2 Real Estate.
					h3 Lead Generation.
					p Generate quality leads for your business with the most easy to use idx search in the industry. Promote yourself while bringing exposure to your listings.
					a(href="#").ib-btn: span Request Demo
					.ib-wrap-img
						img(data-lazy="images/slider-1.jpg").gs-lazy
				article.ib-st-slider-item
					h2 Powered by WordPress.
					h3 Customized by you.
					p You have complete control of your website. Simply click the customize button and change colors, logos, text, and more in seconds.
					a(href="#").ib-btn: span Request Demo
					.ib-wrap-img
						img(data-lazy="images/slider-2.jpg").gs-lazy

		section.ib-section.ib-format-a
			article.ib-wrap-content
				h2.ib-title Real Estate Websites and Lead Generation
				h3.ib-sub-title For Real Estate Professionals
				p Create a stunning website for your market and start generating quality leads for your real estate business today. IDXBoost real estate websites and lead generation programs are design to elevate your digital presence.

			.ib-group-img
				.ib-wrap-img
					img(src="images/pc.png")
					span.ib-label Choose from one 
						span of our beautiful
						|WordPress themes!

		section.ib-section.ib-format-a
			article.ib-wrap-content
				h2.ib-title Hyperttargeted Real Estate Landing Pages
				p Start driving traffic to your online brand with the industry’s most advanced IDX solution. From draw-on-map searches to custom pages for neighborhoods and condo buildings, we give you the technology to keep your clients engaged.
	            
			.ib-group-img
				.ib-wrap-img
					img(src="images/panel-0.png")
    
		section.ib-section.ib-format-b
			article.ib-wrap-content
				h2.ib-title One-click editing.
				h3.ib-sub-title Unlimited options.
				p Simply click the customize button and effortlessly change colors, logos, text, and more in a matter of seconds. Our technology is so easy a flight test monkey could do it.
          
			.ib-group-img
				.ib-wrap-img
					img(src="images/customizer.png") 
		
		section.ib-section.ib-format-a
			article.ib-wrap-content
				h2.ib-title See what your visitors are searching for
				p With our simple visitor dashboard, you can see what properties they saved, neighborhoods and condo buildings they like, and what price range they want. You can even recommend other properties to them!

			.ib-group-img
				.ib-wrap-img
					img(src="images//b-admin.png")

		section.ib-section.ib-format-b
			.ib-wrap-content
				h2.ib-title We work with your favorite 
					span brands and CRMS!
				ul
					li
						h3.ib-list-title Integrate your favorite CRM
						p We work with your favorite CRM. No need to learn a new system. If you are not using one yet we can set you up with one of our favorites.
					li
						h3.ib-list-title Automate your business & marketing
						p Connect your new inbound leads to your favorite channels of distribution. Don’t have one yet? We can help!
					li
						h3.ib-list-title Build a digital resource
						p For you your team or your agency, build your office in the cloud and have access to everything anywhere you go.

				a(href="#").ib-btn: span Request Demo

			.ib-st-slider
